Package nl.naturalis.geneious.util

Class PreconditionValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.geneious.util.PreconditionValidator
  • public class PreconditionValidator
extends Object
    Checks whether the preconditions for an operation (e"g" a BOLD import) are satisfied. There are a few preconditions that need to be checked no matter the operation. Individual operations can request additional checks.
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman

    • Constructor Detail

      • PreconditionValidator

        public PreconditionValidator​(int preconditions)
        Create a PreconditionValidator that checks the provided preconditions. The preconditions are specified using a bitwise OR. E.g. ALL_DOCUMENTS_IN_SAME_DATABASE | VALID_TARGET_FOLDER. If you only want to check operation-independent preconditions, specify BASIC.
        Parameters:
        preconditions -
